OL,5, A new drama is to explore the life of  
OL,6, Justin Fashanu, the first top-flight   
OL,7, professional footballer to come out as 
OL,8, gay. BBC News looks at what the ITV    
OL,9, series may bring to light, two decades 
OL,10, after his untimely death.              
OL,12,FBorn in Hackney, east London, in 1961, 
OL,13,FJustin Fashanu and his younger brother,
OL,14,FJohn, grew up with white foster parents
OL,15,Fnear Attleborough in Norfolk. Aged 13, 
OL,16,Fhe was spotted by a Norwich City talent
OL,17,Fscout while playing for his school team
OL,18,Fand signed as a professional with the  
OL,19,Fclub at 17.                            
